metadata.name: Desi Baby Club
metadata.description: Desi Baby Club is a unique 2D NFT collection of 1500 Indian Babies living on the Ethereum blockchain. Designed by the renowned Indian artist Prasad Bhat.  The art represents rich Indian culture and with the community, we aim to bridge Indian talent and Web3 opportunities. Desi Baby Club holders get access to utilities like Web3 job listings, insights, IRL events, airdrops and much more. Visit desibabyclub.com for more details!
metadata.story: At an altitude of 7491m, on the peak of a mountain in the Himalaya range, lives our Baba baby. He shunned this ancient society on a quest for the perfect world! Already a master of vedas and mantras, he discovered the magic of code! Overcoming the 404, he cracked the power of creating a community of wacky babies led by his top Devotees- who are the pillars for his vision.
